			<dt>What is it?</dt>
			<dd>
				<p>TenDRA is a general purpose C and C++ compiler, and a framework
					for general compiler development.
					Its emphasis is on portability and correctness, which it
					ensures through compiling to a
					<a href="#TODO-tdfspec">formally specified</a> portable
					intermediate representation, XXX;.</p>

				<p>The TenDRA Project, here at <code>tendra.org</code>,
					encompasses both development of the compiler itself and a handful of
					compiler-related supporting utilities.</p>

				<p>See <a href="#TODO">About</a> and the <a href="#TODO">orientation guide</a> for more.</p>
			</dd>

